Fisayo Akinade (amuru 28 Disemba 1987) bu onye omekorita Britain, mara amara maka oru ya dika Dean Monroe na Cucumber na Banana na Channel 4 na Mr
Ajayi na usoro Netflix ama ama Heartstopper, yana oru ya na ihe nkiri.
Ọ nọrọ afọ anọ n'oge ọ bụ nwata na Naịjirịa tupu ọ laghachi UK ebe ọ tolitere na Fallowfield na Moss Side nke Manchester.
